content: I love it, beautiful art work, amazing voice over, user friendly app. I knew I made the right choice in buying the actual card ‚ù§
Love the artwork and i personally have a physical copy of this tarot deck and i adore it

Its a good app. I use it alongside the actual deck so I dont bend the booklet. However I've become a avid user of the journal part and wised there was a edit options. Since I may make one or two spelling mistakes. Other then that its great!
Surprisingly meaningful, it's basically what it says on the tin. Lovely!
Absolutely love this deck! Colorful artwork and good interpretations. Highly recommend!
Beautiful art in this app and I very much enjoy the book author's interpretations.

I really, really, resonate with this deck/app. I think I'm going to buy the physical card set and use both. The artwork is amazing, it captures the essence of the cards well. And the meanings/descriptions alone would be worth the price of the app. Very happy I found this one.

I own Mystical Cat Tarot for 1 year, and just explore the card out of the blue, but suddenly found this deck. I am stunned by the visual of the cards and can tell that I will definitely love this deck. And no regret, I made my right choice. Now I own physical book by the day I bought this app. Love the part of practice. Good point of view in the way to describe the cards meaning. But there is app crashed when I tap to go in "Enter external reading". Would give 5 stars if this bug is fixed.
Has the same issues as the other apps I've reviewed by Fool's Dog, and it works just as well. I wish the journal was easier to use.
perfect tarot deck and app. Worth every penny!
